{"tid":2165194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣指中國黑客入侵台北市政府、大學、網絡服務商的電腦系統","createTime":"2020-08-19T16:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T16:34:59.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d27fa9bce5edd28aaa2d6c60234d64b6438821","tid":2165194,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"台灣調查局表示，10個台灣政府機構以及4家通訊服務供應商遭到駭客攻擊，許多跡象顯示，駭客攻擊來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n調查局資安工作站副主任劉家榮星期三（8月19日）在記者會上說，最近偵辦幾起政府機關遭駭案件，發現駭客攻擊範圍包括台北市政府在內的兩個市政府，水資源局，國立大學等10個單位，以及4家資訊服務供應商；涉及6000多個政府郵件帳號的5台郵件服務器遭植入後門程式，由於駭客會抹除軌跡資料，無法判斷有無資料遭竊，但仍然對資訊安全造成重大威脅，已經成立專案小組偵察辦理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/taiwan-china-behind-cyberattacks-government-agencies-emails-20200819/5549710.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Ftaiwan-china-behind-cyberattacks-government-agencies-emails-20200819%2F5549710.html%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Ddlvr.it&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=baf82824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/taiwan-china-behind-cyberattacks-government-agencies-emails-20200819/5549710.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296115573164609536?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296115573164609536%3Fs%3D20&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a55edde7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296115573164609536%3Fs%3D20&h=7deaf887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296115573164609536?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"3f4560182c85319d036765075b614d1d8e3eec7c","tid":2165194,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2